01:13:16,258 --> 01:13:19,352
He's not all he seems to be

1024
01:13:19,595 --> 01:13:22,996
And that girl
he trails behind him

1025
01:13:23,532 --> 01:13:26,831
Is the child
he stole from me

1026
01:13:27,002 --> 01:13:28,401
Yeah, and me.

1027
01:13:28,570 --> 01:13:29,696
Yeah, both of us.

1028
01:13:29,872 --> 01:13:34,900
(SlNGlNG) Could it be
he's that old jailbird
That the tide now washes in?

1029
01:13:35,077 --> 01:13:39,741
Heard my name
and started running
All the omens point to him

1030
01:13:40,215 --> 01:13:45,414
In the absence of a victim

1031
01:13:46,722 --> 01:13:51,056
Dear Inspector, may I go?

1032
01:13:54,229 --> 01:13:56,129
And remember

1033
01:13:56,698 --> 01:13:57,790
(SPlTS)

1034
01:13:57,866 --> 01:13:59,766
When you've nicked him

1035
01:14:00,602 --> 01:14:06,939
It was me what told you so

1036
01:14:07,776 --> 01:14:10,643
Let the old man
keep on running

1037
01:14:10,813 --> 01:14:15,079
I will run him off his feet!

1038
01:14:17,920 --> 01:14:21,651
Everyone, about your business
Clear this garbage
off the street

1039
01:14:24,293 --> 01:14:28,753
Cosette! Now I remember

1040
01:14:29,665 --> 01:14:33,931
Cosette! How can it be?

1041
01:14:35,070 --> 01:14:39,166
We were children together

1042
01:14:40,509 --> 01:14:45,139
Look what's become of me

1043
01:14:47,783 --> 01:14:50,047
Eponine! Who was that girl?

1044
01:14:50,219 --> 01:14:53,120
That bourgeois
two-a-penny thing

1045
01:14:53,288 --> 01:14:55,222
Eponine, find her for me!

1046
01:14:55,624 --> 01:14:56,955
What will you give me?

1047
01:14:57,125 --> 01:14:58,615
Anything!

1048
01:14:58,794 --> 01:15:03,595
Got you all excited now
But God knows
what you see in her

1049
01:15:03,765 --> 01:15:05,756
Aren't you all delighted now?

1050
01:15:05,934 --> 01:15:10,735
No,
I don't want your money, sir

1051
01:15:13,408 --> 01:15:17,276
Eponine, do this for me

1052
01:15:17,446 --> 01:15:19,812
Discover where she lives

1053
01:15:20,315 --> 01:15:25,651
But careful how you go
Don't let your father know

1054
01:15:26,188 --> 01:15:31,421
Eponine! I'm lost
until she's found

